event.title: Monthly Fellowship meeting in Vienna, Austria

body.p:
For a change, the Vienna Fellowship meeting this month will be at the venue called "Tunnel", located in the Florianigasse 9 in the 8th discrict of Vienna.
We'll be there from 18:00, with agenda related discussions starting at 19:00. As usual, this invitation is for everyone interested in the FSFE or Free Software. We're looking forward to seeing you there!
